then formula_76 converges to formula_2 uniformly if and only if formula_78 as formula_68. Thus, we can characterize uniform convergence of formula_50 on formula_3 as (simple) convergence of formula_50 in the function space formula_83 with respect to the &quot;uniform metric&quot; (also called the supremum metric), defined by 

