=== Exponential function ===
The series expansion of the exponential function can be shown to be uniformly convergent on any bounded subset formula_194 using the Weierstrass M-test.

Theorem (Weierstrass M-test). &quot;Let formula_1 be a sequence of functions formula_196 and let formula_197 be a sequence of positive real numbers such that formula_198 for all formula_21 and formula_200 If formula_201 converges, then formula_202 converges absolutely and uniformly on formula_3.&quot;

